name: QUANTIFIER
value:
case ch:                                                               \
      if (context->stack == bottom)                                      \
      goto CHARACTER;                                                \
      push(context,                                                      \
           &(cregex_node_t) {                                             \
    .type = REGEX_NODE_TYPE_QUANTIFIER,                       \
    .nmin = min,                                              \
    .nmax = max,                                              \
    .greedy = (*context->sp == '?') ? (++context->sp, 0) : 1, \
    .quantified = consume(context) \
  } \
           );                         \
      break
